high_descs: Turn right then walk towards the sink.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle on the left side of the sink.
Turn all the way around then walk towards the wall, turn left towards the table.
Take the knife, then slice the loaf of bread on the table.
Turn left and walk towards the refrigerator, open the door.
Place the knife on the second shelf, then close the door.
Turn left then walk towards the wall, then turn left toward the table.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn left walk towards the refrigerator, turn right.
Open the refrigerator door and place the slice of bread on the third shelf, then close the door. Open the door and remove the slice of bread from the third shelf and close the door.
Turn right and walk towards the sink.
Open the microwave door above the sink and place the slice of bread inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a piece of sliced bread inside of a microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the sink
Grab the large knife that is in front of the sink
Turn around and head to the white table
Cut the loaf of bread on the table into slices
Turn around and head to the fridge
Open the fridge and place the knife on the top rack
Turn around and face the white table
Grab a slice of bread off the table
Turn around and head to the fridge
Open the fridge and place the bread on the middle rack. Close the fridge. Open the fridge and grab the bread.
Turn to your right and head to the microwave
Open the microwave and put the bread inside
anns.task_desc: Putting a slice of bread in the microwave

high_descs: Look down then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn around and walk towards the wall and turn left to face the table.
Use the knife to slice the bread on the table.
Turn left, walk up, and turn left again to open the fridge.
Place the knife inside the fridge and close the door.
Turn left and return to the table.
Pick up the first slice of bread off the table.
Return to the fridge and open the doors.
Place the bread in the fridge and close the doors, then open the doors and take the bread out and close the doors.
Head back towards the kitchen sink.
Put the slice of bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the bread in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife that is in front of the sink on the left side.
Turn all the way around and go to the right side of the white table with the knife.
With the knife slice the bread that is on the table.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the fridge.
While holding the knife open the fridge with other hand.  Place the knife on the second shelf of the fridge.
Turn and go to the right side of the white table.
Pick up a slice of bread that is closest to you.
Turn around with the slice of bread in your hand and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge. Place the bread on the third shelf and shut the fridge door.  Open the fridge door and pick up the bread slice that is on the third shelf.  Shut the door.
Turn with the slice of bread in hand and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave door and place the slice of bread to the left of the object in there.  Shut the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Slice bread to put in microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the seat.
Turn around and walk across the room and face the table on the left.
Cut of the loaf of bread into slices.
Turn around to face the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Turn around and walk over to the bread on the table.
Pick up a slice of the bread.
Turn around to face the fridge.
Put the slice of bread into the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Turn right and walk forward to face the microwave above the sink.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a slice of bread as well as put it in the microwave.
